  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Prepare doner meat by marinating with Soy Sauce, Mirin, and Oyster Sauce for at least 2 hours.",
    "Sauté minced garlic and ginger in oil until fragrant. Add peanuts and almonds; stir-fry until lightly golden.",
    "Pour in marinade from the doner meat and any collected juices. Simmer to allow flavors to meld together.",
    "Add Rice Vinegar and continue simmering for 5 minutes, scraping up all crispy bits from the bottom of the pan.",
    "Toss in sesame seeds and mix well. Adjust seasoning with salt if needed.",
    "Serve hot over rice or noodles."
